    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Doton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 14</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 16</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 30 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 18 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 34</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This difficult and powerful technique has you focus a large amount of Chakra into your hands and touch the ground, sending forth a seemingly subtle shockwave. Immediately after, 15 ft tall stalagmites erupt throughout the area, dealing 8d12 earth damage and leaving a forest of stony trees that resemble a thick forest, not providing enough space for Small-sized or larger creatures to fight in. The stalagmites remain for one day, or until dismissed.<br><br>This technique cannot be performed on water.</p>\n\n\n\n",
